# Antigravity Agent Rules

## Terminal & Environment
- **Operating System**: Windows
- **Preferred Shell**: pwsh (PowerShell 7)
- **Virtual Environment**: This project uses a Python virtual environment located at `E:\nano-claw-public\.venv\`.
- **Python Execution Rules**: 
  - NEVER use the global `python` or `pip` commands unless explicitly requested.
  - DO NOT attempt to run `Activate.ps1` to activate the environment.
  - ALWAYS use the direct executable path relative to the project root (e.g., `.venv\Scripts\python.exe`, `.venv\Scripts\pip.exe`, `.venv\Scripts\pytest.exe`, `.venv\Scripts\ruff.exe`) for all Python-related terminal commands.
